.TH "BEEHIIV-NEWSLETTER-LISTS-GET" "1" "Apr 2026" "beehiiv-cli" "Beehiiv CLI Manual"

.SH NAME
beehiiv-newsletter-lists-get - Get newsletter list Beta OAuth Scope: newsletter_lists:read


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBbeehiiv newsletter-lists get  [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
Get newsletter list Beta OAuth Scope: newsletter_lists:read

.PP
 Newsletter Lists is currently in beta, the API is subject to change. Retrieve a single newsletter list belonging to a specific publication.

.PP
API path: /publications/{publicationId}/newsletter_lists/{newsletterListId}


